{"tid":2013941,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有人刻意將「大虎頭蜂」帶到美國，首次出現在華盛頓","createTime":"2020-05-12T16:07:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T17:24:40.000Z","uid":104138,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7499d12fffe00dcf804abb4430eb8ab2bf8857a4","tid":2013941,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:07:12.000Z","msg":"【#十萬八千里】「大虎頭蜂」原本生於東南亞、中國大陸南方以及台灣，上年首次在美國出現。科學家估計，牠們可能經由國際貨運「偷渡」至華盛頓州港口，亦可能是有人刻意將牠們帶到美國。「大虎頭蜂」會攻擊蜜蜂，只需90分鐘牠們就能佔據蜜蜂的蜂巢，並將幼蜂咬爛成有營養的糊狀物，用以喂飼自己的幼蟲。<br />\n.<br />\n一按即聽節目《十萬八千里》：<a href=\"http://app3.rthk.hk/special/pau/article.php?aid=3961\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapp3.rthk.hk%2Fspecial%2Fpau%2Farticle.php%3Faid%3D3961&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmOaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=837f0783\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://app3.rthk.hk/special/pau/article.php?aid=3961</a>"},{"pid":"1994b3581a09d0f0b7f3097135f184cb014a0557","tid":2013941,"uid":48579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:08:13.000Z","msg":"asshole with wings"},{"pid":"61d09023d11f4a84b26291f3edff85ad0ade1869","tid":2013941,"uid":104138,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"7499d12fffe00dcf804abb4430eb8ab2bf8857a4","tid":2013941,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:07:12.000Z","msg":"【#十萬八千里】「大虎頭蜂」原本生於東南亞、中國大陸南方以及台灣，上年首次在美國出現。科學家估計，牠們可能經由國際貨運「偷渡」至華盛頓州港口，亦可能是有人刻意將牠們帶到美國。「大虎頭蜂」會攻擊蜜蜂，只需90分鐘牠們就能佔據蜜蜂的蜂巢，並將幼蜂咬爛成有營養的糊狀物，用以喂飼自己的幼蟲。<br />\n.<br />\n一按即聽節目《十萬八千里》：<a href=\"http://app3.rthk.hk/special/pau/article.php?aid=3961\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapp3.rthk.hk%2Fspecial%2Fpau%2Farticle.php%3Faid%3D3961&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmOaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=837f0783\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://app3.rthk.hk/special/pau/article.php?aid=3961</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T16:08:56.000Z","msg":"蜜蜂如果減少會造成生態災難，用呢招既人好毒<br />\n唔駛查都知邊個國家做"},{"pid":"c12daa75f793282d49c7552bd6a6afb8